Celebrities and industry friends graced the Sun Arena Times Square in Pretoria on Saturday evening for the much-anticipated DStv Mzansi Viewers Choice Awards after a two-year hiatus Hosted by Big Brother Mzansi and The River Actor Lawrence Maleka, the theme of the night was black-tie or traditional. Here’s our favourite looks from the glamourous night: Pamela Mtanga was one of the DSTV Mzansi Viewers Choice awards blue carpet hosts. She was dressed by Keys Fashion.  Media personality Blue Mbombo rocked a royal yellow Scalo Designer dress.  The Wife and House of Zwide actress Gaisang Noge stole the show with her breathtaking pearl inspired dress, which showed off her gorgeous body. Actress Kwanele Mthethwa kept it safe in a black elegant dress which went well with the theme of the evening.  Sannah Mchunu, who scooped favourite actress, rocked a red number that complimented her curvaceous body. <img class="alignnone wp-image-195728 size-full" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="853" height="1280" srcset="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-scaled.jpg 853w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-167x250.jpg 167w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-533x800.jpg 533w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-696x1044.jpg 696w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-1068x1602.jpg 1068w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/RZ9_1015-280x420.jpg 280w" sizes="(max-width: 853px) 100vw, 853px" />  <img class="alignnone wp-image-195432 size-full" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Connie-MVA-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="1280" hei